  "name": "Enlarge Spell",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/feats/enlarge-spell.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You can increase the range of your spells.</em><br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />You can alter a spell with a range of close, medium, or long to increase its range by 100%. An enlarged spell with a range of close now has a range of 50 ft. + 5 ft./level, while medium-range spells have a range of 200 ft. + 20 ft./level and long-range spells have a range of 800 ft. + 80 ft./level. An enlarged spell uses up a spell slot one level higher than the spell's actual level.<br /><br />Spells whose ranges are not defined by distance, as well as spells whose ranges are not close, medium, or long, do not benefit from this feat.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Usage</strong>: create copies of spells and adjust them.</p>",
